    },
    {
      "comment": "--- Intro ---"
    },
    {
      "say": "Z Z saves and quits. Z Q quits without saving. Two keystrokes, no colon needed."
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.3
    },
    {
      "comment": "--- Demo 1: ZZ to save and quit ---"
    },
    {
      "say": "Make a change first. Change ready to done.",
